{
  "stem": "3382.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Of course, I had some other very unpleasant encounters with-- in the prisoner, I was beaten up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Since then, I have tinnitus in my ear-- in this-- and I lost--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And to-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] on the 17th-- it seems so, yes-- of September, to my big surprise, I received a package.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From whom?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I started to know-- so I said, maybe there is something that-- and the bread was cut in pieces.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in one of the pieces, I felt a paper.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There is a thin cigarette paper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said-- and this is Kzarnowski, the supervisor from the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, Meljinski, Jews from Lida ghetto transported the 18th.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Tell that you are a Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know what to do on the transport in Polish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next day, I was taken for interrogation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Are you Jewish?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Look, I said, sir, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you beat me, and anyways, otherwise you'll shot me, kill me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You want to tell that I am Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I tell that I am Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can tell you even if you want to-- I'll tell you anything you want.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ha ha, sign it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I read, you know, a stupid paper that I was arrested on suspicion that I am a Polish partisans but turn out that I am Jewish who from free will admitted that he is Jewish-- nothing that-- I signed it-- I send it back.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] At that time, I had to bury during the so-called dinner time, when [NON-ENGLISH] who brought in the big soup, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He hit me [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with the-- with a stick.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he try to hit my head.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he hit me here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The stick-- that stick, you know, it's a two-by-four, or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Broke in two.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
